cs.CR, cs.SI, cs.DB, cs.MM, cs.IR

This paper discusses the use of mobile ad networks to track user location, which is a security and privacy concern, making cs.CR (Security and Privacy) the most likely category. The paper also involves data management and analysis, which could fall under cs.DB (Databases) and cs.IR (Information Retrieval). Additionally, the paper discusses the use of mobile apps and ad libraries, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
